about.title: About me
about.text: I am a determined and motivated software enthusiast with a passion for continuous learning and growth. My experience includes team leadership, critical thinking, and problem-solving gained through coursework and collaborative projects. Proficient in core algorithms, data structures, and design patterns, I am eager to contribute my skills and knowledge to advance in software development. I am excited about the opportunities that lie ahead in my career.
